[Body]
== Description ==
Array Increment is an application that takes three different arrays and increases them a number of given times. The purpose of this application is to show parallelism between the different increments. 


== Execution instructions ==
Usage:
runcompss --project=project_localhost_XXX.xml --lang=python <install_path>/array_increment_mpi/arrayi-increment.py <number_of_increments> <initArrayValue1> <initArrayValue2> <initArrayValue3>

where:
		 * - N: Number of times to increase the counters
		 * - initValue1: Initial value for array counter 1
                 * - initValue2: Initial value for array counter 2
                 * - initValue3: Initial value for array counter 3


== Execution Example ==
runcompss --project=project_localhost_1.4.xml --lang=python <install_path>/array_increment_mpi/array-increment.py 2 [1,2,3] [4,5,6] [7,8,9]


== Build ==
cd mpi
mpicc -lm mpi_vector_inc.c -o mpi_vector
modify project_localhost_XXX.xml seting the AppDir to the <install_path>


